偏态系数。</p><p>对汉江流域上游三个水文分区，区域线性矩参数计算成果如表6所示。</p><p>根据区域线性矩参数，可以计算得P-III型分布参数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2410396x102_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2410396x103_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2410396x104_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的区域估计值，确定区域频率曲线<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2410396x105_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。经计算，各水文分区基于P-III型频率分布曲线的区域增长曲线成果如表7和图1所示。</p></sec><sec id="s5_7"><title>3.7. 区域设计洪水</title><p>对任一站点，推求概率<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2410396x106_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>所对应的设计洪峰流量采用公式(4)计算，区域增长曲线<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2410396x107_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>已经得出，指标洪</p><table-wrap id="table3" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table3">Table 3</xref></label><caption><title> Identification result of hydrological homogeneous region</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >站名</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >茶店子</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >铁锁关</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >元墩</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >三华石</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >南沙河</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >江西营</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >升仙村</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >长滩村</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >组别</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >III</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >I</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >II</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >II</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >II</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >II</td><td align="center"